					<outline text="trying to fix it &lt;a href=&quot;http://blog.liip.ch/archive/2007/04/25/if-you-spill-coffee-on-your-macbook-pro-2.html&quot;&gt;probly don't work too well&lt;/a&gt;." created="Tue, 10 Jul 2007 20:28:27 GMT"/>
